<br>
Reminds me a bit of the male/female tennis match way back (in the 70's). Something to stir the pot, get folks who would never dream of watching the sport interested in the &quot;political&quot; aspect of matching men against woman.<br>
<br>
All that being said, I have heard she is so far beyond the rest of the women pro's that she is kinda bored with the LPGA, so maybe she told them &quot; let me play once with the boys, or I take my toys and go home&quot;.<br>
<br>
It will be interesting to see how high up the leader board she can get...<br>
<br>
...now if I could only get myself into a 4-some with 3 LPGA gals. I'd show them that sometimes the more strokes the better.<br>
